    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Seprevois evolved from the simian creatures of their home world (see page 50). They are covered in fine, short hair ranging in color from dark brown to pale blond, except for the black skin of their faces and hands. Seprevois have six elongated fingers on each hand, each featuring an additional joint compared to a human\u2019s hand. Seprevois\u2019 four feet have three unjointed toes each."
        }
